===Adverb===
'''only'''
# without others or anything [[further]]; [[exclusively]]
#: ''my heart is hers, and hers '''only'''''
# no more than; just
#: ''if there were '''only''' one more ticket!''
# as recently as
#: ''he left '''only''' moments ago'' 

